 VASTRA Collection: A Visual Symphony of Culture and Grace
Brand Essence:
VASTRA isn’t just a clothing brand—it’s a celebration of heritage, femininity, and artistic flair. The name itself evokes the richness of Indian textiles, while your design choices reflect a contemporary twist on timeless beauty.
Logo Design:
- A graceful girl in a saree, framed in a circular motif with soft brown lines—symbolizing continuity, tradition, and warmth.
